title: State football polls

Posted: 2:23 p.m. Monday, Oct. 19, 2015 State football polls View Larger MARC PENDLETON / STAFF Fairmont QB Corde’ Kyles unloads under pressure from Alden Simms of Alter in their season opener on Aug. 28.
